<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13905</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>派对后，除了小美人鱼，船上的人们都去睡了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30430</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她知道自己在日出的时候会变成大海的泡沫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30431</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35692</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以，她呆在甲板上，看着大海和星星。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35693</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43789</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的王子，我的灵魂和我的未来，现在都没了。” 她想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43790</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51090</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在太阳升起的几分钟前，小美人鱼发现水里有东西在动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51091</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，她看见五个人影从海里出来，向她挥手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼没能马上认出来她的姐姐们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62043</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们又长又美的头发不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65581</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69432</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们一起游近小美人鱼站的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69433</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75516</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们说话时，她们的头在水面上下浮动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79278</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们来这儿救你！” 大姐大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79279</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们一听说王子的婚礼，就马上去找海巫婆寻求帮助。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85183</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>二姐解释说：“她给了我们一个魔法匕首，能救你的命。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95214</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>作为交易，她要走了我们的头发。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95215</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>三姐告诉小美人鱼海巫婆叫她们做什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105632</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在太阳升起前，你必须用匕首杀死王子，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105633</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110328</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只要他死了，你就能再变回人鱼。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110329</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113396</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼颤抖着身体。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113397</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118029</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可是，我不能杀死我的王子。” 她想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118030</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123854</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当小美人鱼犹豫时，四姐接着说：“求你了，妹妹。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123855</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126027</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你必须杀了他救自己。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126028</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，你就能跟我们回家了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129187</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134992</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>五姐替所有人鱼说：“我们都很想你。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134993</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奶奶和爸爸都在等你。你属于海底王国。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可是，我希望我的人生会不一样。” 小美人鱼伤心地想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153595</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大姐忍不住大喊：“快！你必须要快。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153596</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157596</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天就要亮了。现在就杀了那个王子！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157597</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160181</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她向空中扔出匕首。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160182</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164531</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼很容易地就接住了那把匕首。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164532</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妹妹，求你快点！” 五个人鱼大喊着，潜回了水底。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼看着那把匕首。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177854</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她不知道该怎么办。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177855</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182144</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这个礼物让姐姐们失去了美丽的头发。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182145</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186704</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们给了她最后的机会救自己。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186705</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192814</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼走到王子的帐篷前，拉开了门帘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192815</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她轻轻地走了进去，看见他的王子搂着他的新娘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199655</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202683</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们睡得很沉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202684</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼觉得又恨又爱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213260</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>透过帐篷薄薄的布，她看见早晨的太阳就要升起来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213261</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218482</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没有时间了。她最后的机会就要消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218483</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看了看匕首，然后看了看熟睡的王子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227762</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>要么她活，要么王子活。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227763</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把匕首放低，靠近他的心脏，但又停了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233587</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236490</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我怎么能杀了他呢？” 她想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236491</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我爱我的王子。他必须活着，即使我必须死。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以，小美人鱼跑出帐篷，把匕首扔进了大海。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253926</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，她跳进了大海。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253927</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260780</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她能感觉到她的身体化成了数千个大海泡沫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260781</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269139</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，小美人鱼就不存在了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>